# DataVisualizer Pro

A professional-grade, automated Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) tool built with Python and Streamlit. This application transforms raw datasets into interactive visual dashboards while providing technical health audits and preprocessing recommendations.

## Core Features

* **Automated Data Audit:** Instant reporting on dataset dimensions, missing values, and duplicate rows.
* **Imbalance Detection:** Real-time analysis of target variable distributions with automated alerts for minority class skewness.
* **Intelligent Visualization Engine:** A rule-based plotting system that automatically selects the optimal chart type (Scatter, Box, Histogram, or Heatmap) based on feature dimensionality and data types.
* **Expert Recommendations:** Actionable insights for data cleaning and modeling strategies based on detected data quality issues.
* **Interactive Dark Interface:** A high-contrast, professional UI designed for technical environments.

## Project Architecture

The project follows a modular "separation of concerns" design:

```text
DataVisualizer/
├── src/
│   ├── analyzer.py     
│   ├── loader.py      
│   ├── visualizer.py   
│   └── recommender.py  
├── app.py              
└── requirements.txt    